/* 7 Slice vs Splice */

/* Slice 
	
  1] Does not modifies the original array (Immutable).
  2] Useful for to select/pick the specified elements from an array.
  3] Returns the subset of array.
	
*/


/* Splice
	1] Does modifies the original array.
  2] useful for deletion/insertion of an element in an array.
  3] Returns the deleted elements as array.
*/
